Historical Daily Cases and Deaths by Race for Indiana

Source: R/data.R
ind_race_complete.Rd

Raw data that shows daily case and death counts by race.

ind_race_complete

Format

An object of class spec_tbl_df (inherits from tbl_df, tbl, data.frame) with 4160 rows and 58 columns.
